dspace-development.title: `null` Bitstreams are appended (erroneously) for DataSpace Items
Append co-authors for Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering Senior Theses in DataSpace
Orangelight Document https://catalog.princeton.edu/catalog/11873159 does not render the link to the DataSpace Collection

comments.body:
Comparing this to a case in which the DataSpace ARK *was* successfully indexed, the MARC for both records appears to be identical for the Voyager records:

- https://catalog.princeton.edu/catalog/12229858
- https://catalog.princeton.edu/catalog/11873159

Using BibData, the Voyager records encode the following:

- https://bibdata.princeton.edu/bibliographic/12229858
- https://bibdata.princeton.edu/bibliographic/11873159

```xml
<datafield ind1="4" ind2="0" tag="856">
    <subfield code="u">http://arks.princeton.edu/ark:/88435/dsp012v23vx311</subfield>
</datafield>
```
compared to
```xml
<datafield ind1="4" ind2="0" tag="856">
    <subfield code="u">http://arks.princeton.edu/ark:/88435/dsp01w3763983s</subfield>
</datafield>
```

The Solr transformation also shows that these are comparable:

```javascript
electronic_access_1display: [
"{"http://arks.princeton.edu/ark:/88435/dsp01w3763983s": ["arks.princeton.edu"]}"
],
```

```javascript
electronic_access_1display: [
"{"http://gateway.proquest.com/openurl?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&rft_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:dissertation&res_dat=xri:pqm&rft_dat=xri:pqdiss:22624299": ["gateway.proquest.com"],
"http://arks.princeton.edu/ark:/88435/dsp012v23vx311": ["arks.princeton.edu"]}"
],
```
